I"<p>This is investment dressing that won’t break the bank or tie you to one look or season
You all know how much I love summer but I am so happy to see the seasons changing. The reason? Look what I found in <a href="https://www.massimodutti.com/mt" target="_blank">Massimo Dutti</a>.</p>

<p><img src="/images/fashion/massimo-dutti/massimo-dutti-6.jpg" alt="massimo-dutti-6.jpg" /></p>

<p>I say ‘thoughtful’ because of the incredible thought that has gone into the design of these one-pieces and bikinis. The sizing is perfect and clearly the designers understand women’s bodies - and minds - as the adjustable straps mean that not only can you tan safely and evenly, but you choose just how much skin you want to show and how to show it.</p>

