<p>The current collection ‘Fuse’ is very stylish. One- pieces are elegantly sexy and hugely flattering. Bikinis have a reversible design so you get two looks for one. Bikini bottoms comprise classic triangle, Brazilian or ‘Cheeky’ and there’s a range of matching bandeau and triangular tops. Offering XS to 2XL, every size and shape can look great in <a href="https://www.morninggloryswimwear.com/" target="_blank">Morning Glory</a>.</p>

<p><img src="/images/fashion/morning-glory-swimwear/morning-glory-19.jpg" alt="morning-glory-19.jpg" /></p>

